{
  "stem": "521.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And since my father was fairly well-to-do, I didn't need the money, so where I was employed, I was told, you don't need the money, let another Jew-- poor Jew have your job.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I asked myself-- Now, then I was employed by private individuals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All I had to do, to have a piece of paper to show in case they catch me on the street of Budapest, that I'm employed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If-- if they catch-- they caught me, and I could show that I'm employed, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If I couldn't show that I'm employed, then I would have been taken into the concentration camp much earlier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the worse?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I was in a concen-- in as a forced laborer, then by that time, I was just with Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jews--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943, October.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken to Transylvania to the very end of the country, and the name of the place was Bereck-- it's B as in Bob, E-R-E-C-K.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, we were employed by digging ditches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, we had to produce so much-- so much dirt, or sand, or whatnot a day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you couldn't do it, then we had to stay out later in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you went out to-- and when we went home too late on that day, we didn't get any supper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's-- that's the story of the employment.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
